name: Ondo from Ethereum
description: Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0xfAbA6f8e4a5E8Ab82F62fe7C39859FA577269BE3. Ondo Finance is a decentralized investment banking protocol consisting of on-chain financial products that connect investors with capital demand broadening access, improving transparency, and reducing cost versus the status quo. The ONDO token will govern the Ondo Finance protocol.
